  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must have a token on the scene to use this spell (Warpgate mutation limitation).</p><p>This will filter sidebar actors from a folder, default \"Familiars\". Can be changed in the item's configuration.</p><p>After casting this spell a new feature called \"Find Familiar - Attack\" will be available in your features. Use this before attacking with a spell of range touch for it to be cast from the familiar.</p><p>After casting this spell a new feature called \"Find Familiar - Pocket Dimension\" will be available in your features. Use this feature to dismiss and summon the familiar. This works between scenes and will delete left-behind familiar tokens. Deleted familiar tokens will also be tracked. Health will be retained. The pocket dimension feature will revert when the familiar token is deleted and is at 0 hp.</p><p>If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" these will automatically be favorited.</p><p>If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" these will be in it's own section called \"Spell Features.\"</p>",
